data.name: Summer of Loggins
data.description:
This summer, Professor of Rock and Kenny Loggins will team up to tell the story behind some of Kenny’s greatest hits. We’re calling it the Summer of Loggins… so stay tuned! We’ll release a new video each Tuesday afternoon!

To finish off the Summer of Loggins, Professor of Rock will hold a live event on Saturday, October 6th at the beautiful Sand Hollow Resort in St. George, Utah.

We’re also on the hunt for Kenny’s biggest fan. Enter the contest to win free tickets, roundtrip airfare, and accommodations for two on our Facebook fan page.
